project_descr: Strengthening the Capacity of national Volunteer infrastucture for HIV and AIDS response in Swaziland

outputs.output_descr: The project aims to build capacities through volunteerism, provide technical support, training and mentoring skills in strengthening the coordination, management and operations of CSO’s and other multi-sectoral responses to HIV and AIDS.

project_title: strengthening the capacity of national volunteer in swd
